        "abstract": "This course provides a gentle and fun introduction to the theory and practice of interface design for creating and performing music. Our intended audience consists of those who are interested in starting projects relating to music technology. Those with a general interest are also welcome. Participants will learn key aspects of the theory and practice of musical interface design, sufficient to begin to create their own original new musical interfaces.  ",
